Package clui

This package contains the clui command classes of the system (ie the LogIn, LogOut, RegisterRestaurant, RegisterCustomer, RegisterCourier, AddDishRestaurantMenu, ReateMeal, LogaddDish2MealOut, RemoveItemFromMeal, ShowMeal, SaveMeal, SetSpecialOffer, RemoveSepcialOffer, CreateOrder, AddItem2Order, AddMeal2Order, EndOrder, OnDuty, OffDuty, FindDeliverer, SetDeliveryPolicy, SetProfitPolicy, AssociatedCard, ShowListOfOrdersCompleted, ShowCourierDeliveries, ShowCouriersRegistered, ShowRestaurantsRegistered, ShowRestaurantTop, ShowCustomers, ShowMenuItem, ShowTotalProfit, ShowTotalProfit, GetParameterToTargetProfit, InitCore classes), responsible for processing user's commands of the MyFoodora system.

Package clui Description

This package contains the clui command classes of the system (ie the LogIn, LogOut, RegisterRestaurant, RegisterCustomer, RegisterCourier, AddDishRestaurantMenu, ReateMeal, LogaddDish2MealOut, RemoveItemFromMeal, ShowMeal, SaveMeal, SetSpecialOffer, RemoveSepcialOffer, CreateOrder, AddItem2Order, AddMeal2Order, EndOrder, OnDuty, OffDuty, FindDeliverer, SetDeliveryPolicy, SetProfitPolicy, AssociatedCard, ShowListOfOrdersCompleted, ShowCourierDeliveries, ShowCouriersRegistered, ShowRestaurantsRegistered, ShowRestaurantTop, ShowCustomers, ShowMenuItem, ShowTotalProfit, ShowTotalProfit, GetParameterToTargetProfit, InitCore classes), responsible for processing user's commands of the MyFoodora system. It also implements CommandProcessor interface required for the Strategy pattern. It also implements the CluiLauncher class to be used by a future system tester. required for the Observer pattern. It also implements StringCast class to cast input strings to command's argument type requirements.
Author:
Pedro León, Juan Castillo
